criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria includes

          -  (1) Women of Hispanic origin;

          -  (2) established patient of the neurology clinic defined as clinic visits at the
             LAC/USC Neurology Clinic that have spanned greater than one year;

          -  (3) age > 30

          -  (4) willing and able to utilize a Fitbit activity Monitor;

          -  (5) own a smart phone device;

          -  (6) ambulatory without assistance;

          -  (7) willing and able to provide informed consent;

          -  (8) within commuting distance to the wellness center and LAC/USC hospital;

          -  (9) reads or comprehends Spanish;

          -  (10) weekly internet access.

        Exclusion Criteria includes

          -  (1) Clinically significant neurological or psychiatric illness including mental
             retardation, dementia or severe depression/anxiety;

          -  (2) any physical condition that precludes engagement in exercise, including
             significant heart disease.
